Class BeanTestFact

  • public class BeanTestFact
extends java.lang.Object
    A Java Pojo for the express purpose of testing the behavior of compilation and execution of rules. This class should not be included in the released artifact, if it did make it into a released artifact it should be ignored and not consumed as it may be moved/removed without warning to consumers.
